
===================================
📌 1. Finglish Version (Persian Latin Script)
===================================

📖 **Tashrih:**
    Dastoor `fwupdate` baraye update kardan ya tagheer dadane firmware device-ha estefade mishavad. Firmware barname-haye asasi hastand ke sakht-afzar (hardware) ra control mikonand. In dastoor obdat kardan (update) firmware device-ha ra asan mikonad.

⚙️ **Gozine-ha:**
    🔹 `fwupdate --list`  --> 📜 List kardan device-haye ghabele update.
    🔹 `fwupdate <device> <firmware_file>` --> ⬆️ Update kardane firmware yek device moshakhas ba estefade az yek file.
    🔹 `fwupdate --verbose` --> 📢 Namayeshe etela'ate bishtar dar morede process update.

🛠 **Mesal-ha:**

    $ fwupdate --list

    🔹 List kardan hameye device-haye ghabele update.

    $ fwupdate /dev/sda firmware.bin

    🔹 Update kardane firmware device `/dev/sda` ba estefade az file `firmware.bin`.

✅ **Mesal sade:**

    $ fwupdate --verbose /dev/sdb new_firmware.img

    🔹 Update kardane device `/dev/sdb` ba file `new_firmware.img` va namayeshe etela'ate bishtar dar morede process update.

===================================
📌 2. English Version
===================================

📖 **Description:**
    The `fwupdate` command is used to update or modify the firmware of devices. Firmware are essential programs that control hardware. This command simplifies the process of updating device firmware.

⚙️ **Options:**
    🔹 `fwupdate --list` --> 📜 List updatable devices.
    🔹 `fwupdate <device> <firmware_file>` --> ⬆️ Update the firmware of a specific device using a file.
    🔹 `fwupdate --verbose` --> 📢 Display more information about the update process.

🛠 **Examples:**

    $ fwupdate --list

    🔹 List all devices that can be updated.

    $ fwupdate /dev/sda firmware.bin

    🔹 Update the firmware of the device `/dev/sda` using the `firmware.bin` file.

✅ **Simple Example:**

    $ fwupdate --verbose /dev/sdb new_firmware.img

    🔹 Update the device `/dev/sdb` with the file `new_firmware.img` and display more information about the update process.

